e=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wrapped in simple old school pixel art and fueled by unhinged surge of action, Core Trials may look simple, but it’s anything but. Hesitation means defeat. Learn, adapt, and rise, only those who master body, mind, and core will endure.</p>",
